OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFog patches will clear across
OL,6,FEngland and Wales to leave a warm and
OL,7,Fsunny day here. Cloudier skies for
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland, southern Scotland
OL,9,Fand perhaps northern England, with
OL,10,Fsome light rain possible. Sunshine and
OL,11,Fshowers for the rest of Scotland.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear, with a few fog patches
OL,14,Fforming during the early hours.
OL,15,FThicker cloud across southern Scotland
OL,16,Fmay give the odd spot of light rain.
OL,17,FTurning chilly, with a rural frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
